title: Post Super Bowl Notebook Dump
itunes:title: Post Super Bowl Notebook Dump
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe take you through all the storylines from the "notebook" of the past week after the Super Bowl including birds, cryptic instagram posts, and franchise tags. Gregg needs to meet his plumber.
